INSERT INTO `Section` VALUES (1,'Daily Attitude of my Heart - Sacrifice','I present my body as a living sacrifice, holy & acceptable to YOU, which is my spiritual worship & reasonable service.','Romans 12:1-2','God is attracted to weakness. He can’t resist those who humbly and honestly admit how desperately they need Him. Jim Cymbola',1,NULL,1,'I present myself as a living sacrifice before YOU, Spirit fill & control me.','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NvAiO12cAQs'),(2,'Daily Attitude of my Heart - Focus','YOU have told me that if I wish to follow YOU, I must deny myself, take up my cross daily & follow YOU.','Luke 9:23',NULL,2,NULL,1,'Deny my self centered life. I recognize that I need to deny my own \"justified\" feelings and rights.','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tw8-g7a3T7k'),(3,'Daily Attitude of my Heart - Obey','By this I know if I have come to know YOU, if I keep YOUR commandments.','1 John 2:3',NULL,3,NULL,1,'I will get up & put into action what YOU have called me to do, saying, \"Not my will, but thine\"',NULL),(4,'Daily Attitude of my Heart - Thoughts','FIX my thoughts on what is true, honorable, right, pure, lovely, & admirable. I choose to think about things that are excellent & worthy of praise.','Phil 4:8','Take thoughts & feelings captive.',4,NULL,1,'Help me take thoughts & feelings captive that are not of faith.','https://songselect.ccli.com/search/themes'),(5,'My Father in Heaven','Look at the birds of the air; they do not sow, reap or store away in barns, and yet YOU, my heavenly FATHER feeds them. Am I not much more valuable than they?','Matt 6:26',NULL,5,NULL,1,'My earthly father was not perfect, but YOU are!','https://songselect.ccli.com/search/themes'),(6,'I exalt & glorify YOUR holy Name','Come back, we beg you, O God of Heaven\'s Armies. Look down from heaven and see our plight. Take care of this grapevine','Ps 80:14',NULL,6,NULL,1,'YOU are: HOLY, HOLY, HOLY is the Lord God almighty! Commander of the Armies of Heaven: How cool is that!','tremble-mosaic mcs'),(7,'YOUR Nature','FATHER, YOUR thoughts are not my thoughts, neither are your ways my ways. For as the heavens are higher than the earth, so are YOUR ways higher than mine ways & YOUR thoughts than my thoughts.','Is 55:8, 9',NULL,7,NULL,1,'I worship because YOU are: Transcendent',NULL),(8,'Scripture reading',NULL,'Psalms',NULL,8,NULL,1,'Read 1 Chapter in the Psalms',NULL),(9,'Yeild to YOU','YOUR Kingdom come, YOUR will be done on earth & in my life as it is in Heaven.','Mat 6:10',NULL,9,NULL,1,'Show me where YOU are at work today and bless me to join YOU there.',NULL),(10,'Wait on YOU','I wait for YOU, my soul waits, in YOUR word I hope; my soul waits for YOU more than watchmen for the morning.','Ps 130:5, 6',NULL,10,NULL,1,'I am waiting & consciously pausing so YOU can take the lead today.',NULL),(11,'Recognize my sin & idoltry','Let no sin reign in my mortal body, to make me obey its passions.','Is 44:9 Lisa Bevere',NULL,11,NULL,1,'An idol is anything you draw your strength from or give your strength to. It is how you spend yourself—your time, your efforts, your thoughts. It is the driving force behind your actions. Of such things, Scripture says: The fashioners of an image—all of them are emptiness, and the things they delight in cannot profit.',NULL),(12,'Recognize & replace','Put on: TENDERHEARTED FORGIVNESS: I will be kind and compassionate to others, forgiving them just as YOU forgave me.','Eph. 4:32','Search me, O God, and know my heart! Try me and know my thoughts',12,NULL,1,'You don’t have to go to heathen lands today to find false gods. America is full of them. Whatever you love more than God is your idol. D.L. Moody','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=82YsmSmekv0'),(13,'Repent','The end of the matter; all has been heard. I will fear God and keep his commandments, for this is the whole duty of man.','Ecclesiastes 12:13 ESV','What specifically do I need to make clean right now?',13,NULL,1,'If I confess my sins, YOU are faithful & just & will forgive my sins & purify me from all unrighteousness. I will fail like a just man seven time (over & over) and I will rise up again and walk in forgiveness. 1 John 1:9',NULL),(14,'Release','For to this you were called, because Christ also suffered for us, leaving us an example, that you should follow His steps: “Who committed no sin, Nor was deceit found in His mouth”; who, when He was reviled, did not revile in return; when He suffered, He did not threaten, but committed Himself to Him who judges righteously; who Himself bore our sins in His own body on the tree, that we, having died to sins, might live for righteousness; by whose stripes you were healed. For you were like sheep going astray, but have now returned to the Shepherd and Overseer of your souls.','1 Peter 2:21-25 NKJV',NULL,14,NULL,1,'I sacrifice to YOU my sin so YOU can replace it with YOUR love. I sign over my title deed of ownership for these sins, & release them to YOU.',NULL),(15,'Scripture reading',NULL,'Proverbs',NULL,15,NULL,1,'Read 1 Chapter in the Proverbs',NULL),(16,'Pray for One Another','I have not ceased to pray & make special request for ____, that we all may be filled with the full knowledge of YOUR will in all wisdom, understanding & discernment of spiritual things.','Rom 12:16','Help me to live in harmony with others.',16,NULL,1,'Help me not be so proud that I don\'t enjoy the company of ordinary people while acting like I know it all! May YOU, who gives this patience & encouragement, help me live in complete harmony with others as fitting for followers of Christ Jesus.',NULL),(17,'Pray for salvation of others','“For God so loved the world, that he gave his only Son, that whoever believes in him should not perish but have eternal life.','John 3:16 ESV','Holy Spirit open eyes of _________________',17,NULL,1,'may these people stand before YOU as Father not as judge. “For God so loved the world, that he gave his only Son, that whoever believes in him should not perish but have eternal life.',NULL),(18,'Spouse','I as a wife does not have authority over my own body but yields it to my husband. In the same way, Husbands do not have authority over my own body but yields it to me his wife.\nMy wife does not have authority over her own body but yields it to me her husband. In the same way, I do not have authority over my own body but yields it to my wife.','SoS 2:16',NULL,18,NULL,1,'Adoration -My beloved is mine and I am theirs.',NULL),(19,'Kids in my life (current or future).','Pray my children, will obey their parents in the Lord, for this is right. “May they honor their father and mother”—because this commandment has a promise— “so that it may go well with them and that they may enjoy long life on the earth.','Acts 16:31 \nEph 6:1-2','Pray my children, will obey their parents in the Lord, for this is right. “May they honor their father and mother”—because this commandment has a promise— “so that it may go well with them and that they may enjoy long life on the earth. Eph 6:1-2',19,NULL,1,'For all the kids, may they have a passion for YOUR Scriptures. May my kids walk in YOUR BELIEF -As they believe in the Lord Jesus, they will be saved.',NULL),(20,'Pray for:','YOU desire all people to be saved & to come to the knowledge of the truth.','1 Tim 2:4','Navy, pastor, pvf donors, PVF Board',20,NULL,1,'Leadership I am accountable to.',NULL),(21,'Scripture reading',NULL,'OT',NULL,21,NULL,1,'Read 1 Chapter in the OT',NULL),(22,'Personal -Blessings','May the words of my mouth and the meditation of my heart be pleasing to you, O LORD, my rock and my redeemer.','Mat 6:11\nPs. 19:14',NULL,22,NULL,1,'Give me today my daily bread.',NULL),(23,'Personal -specific issues','But the tax collector stood at a distance. He would not even look up to heaven, but beat his breast and said, \'God, have mercy on me, a sinner.\' I tell you that this man, rather than the other, went home justified before God. For everyone who exalts himself will be humbled, and he who humbles himself will be exalted.','Luke 18:13-14','I humble myself under YOUR mighty Hand & cast up to YOU these specific matters, becasue I know YOU care for me (1 Pet 5:6-8) and I come in the merits of JESUS alone to make my case that in these items YOU would receive glory and I would receive YOUR good gifts for me.',23,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),(24,'Personal -$$','The rich rules over the poor, and the borrower is the slave of the lender. So I choose freedom and will get and stay out of all debt, no excuses!','Proverbs 22:7',NULL,24,NULL,1,'Help me manage the resources YOU have given me stewardship over according to YOUR truth.',NULL),(25,'Personal -power of my words','Dear children, let us not love with words or speech but with actions and in truth.','1 John 3:18',NULL,25,NULL,1,'Help me be careful what comes out of my mouth.','song words can lift you up and words can tear you down'),(26,'Personal -Who am I?','I am led by the Spirit of God and I am a child of God.','Rom 8:14','How much would life be different if I lived by God\'s veiw of me in JESUS?',26,NULL,1,'I am a child of God.','Lauren daigle-YOU say'),(27,'My Life Purpose','For I am YOUR workmanship, created in YOU for good works, which YOU prepared beforehand, that I should walk in YOU.','Eph 2:10','Who is God to me?',27,NULL,1,'God is, God is near, God is love, Longing to communicate HIMself to me. God the Almighty One Who worketh all in all, is even now waiting to work in me, and make HIMself known. -Andrew Murray',NULL),(28,'Thanks','Let YOUR peace rule in my heart, which I was called in one body to be thankful. Let YOUR word dwell in me richly, teaching & admonishing me in all wisdom, singing psalms & hymns & spiritual songs, with thankfulness in my heart to YOU. And whatever I do, in word or deed, may I do everything in YOUR name Lord Jesus, giving thanks to YOU God the Father.','Col 3:15-17',NULL,28,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),(29,'Scripture reading',NULL,'NT',NULL,29,NULL,1,'Read 1 Chapter in the NT',NULL),(30,'Warfare','Help me be watchful for enemy threat.','1 Corinthians 6:18','May I not face tempation today and deliver me from the enemy that seeks to lie to me and get me to cooperate with the killing, stealing and destroying of everything good YOU desire to bring to my life.',30,NULL,1,'I will flee from sexual immorality. Every other sin I commit is outside the body, but the sexually immoral is a sin against my own body.',NULL),(31,'Armor On!','Cloth me with YOUR whole armor today including my feet with the agile readiness that comes from the Gospel of Peace so I can stand firm against attack, move quickly to gain ground & spread truth wherever I go. Maneuver in battle or die. \"I\'m up, they see me, I\'m down.\"','James 4:7','Submit yourselves to God. Resist the devil, and he will flee from you.',31,NULL,1,'Put on the armor of God.',NULL),(32,'Journal','YOU paid attention & heard me, & a book of remembrance was written before YOU of those who feared YOU & esteemed YOUR name.','Mal 3:16',NULL,32,NULL,1,'Journal what You said to me today:',NULL),(33,'Benidiction for my day','In this way bless one another. *Jehovah bless me & keep me. *Jehovah make YOUR face shine upon me & be gracious to me. *Jehovah lift up YOUR face to me & give me peace.','Num 6:23-26',NULL,33,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),(34,'Music with meaning.','I will sing to YOU, I will sing praises to YOUR name; I will lift up a song to YOU who rides through the deserts; YOUR name is the Lord; I will exalt YOU!','Psalm 68:4',NULL,34,NULL,1,'Listen to songs that draw me close to YOU all day.','https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLZdpE0NYhNb8oTRuuAgPt6OG0SuWcMZUK'),(35,'Pray for specific people.',NULL,NULL,'Customer user input will soon be available here.',35,NULL,1,'Who would you have me pray for right now? (fill names in below)',NULL),(36,'Forgivness','Forgive me of my sins in the exact same way I forgive those that have sinned against me.','Mat 6:12',NULL,36,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),(37,'My List',NULL,NULL,NULL,37,NULL,1,'This will be a list of people I am praying for.',NULL),(38,'Worship & Praise -YOUR Name',NULL,'Matthew 6:9',NULL,38,NULL,1,'I exalt & glorify YOUR holy Name:',NULL),(39,'Replace my way with YOUR way, I receive:',NULL,NULL,'Custom user input will soon be available here.',39,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),(40,'Personal Requests','Brothers, if anyone is caught in any transgression, you who are spiritual should restore him in a spirit of gentleness. Keep watch on yourself, lest you too be tempted. Bear one another\'s burdens, and so fulfill the law of Christ. For if anyone thinks he is something, when he is nothing, he deceives himself.','Galatians 6:1-3',NULL,40,NULL,1,'list burdens & concerns I am praying for:',NULL),(41,'Daily Attitude of my Heart - Sacrifice','The sacrifices YOU desire from me are a broken spirit and contrite heart, O God, YOU will not despise.','Psalm 51:17',NULL,1,NULL,2,'I present myself as a living sacrifice, FATHER may your love flow to and through me.','Don Harris / Marty J Nystrom - A Broken Spirit'),(42,'Daily Attitude of my Heart - Focus','Jesus said to them, \"If anyone wishes to come after ME, he must deny himself, take up his cross & follow Me.\" So today, I choose YOU over my own priorities.','Mark 8:34',NULL,2,NULL,2,'it\'s not about me, it\'s about YOU!',NULL),(43,'Daily Attitude of my Heart - Obey','When all has been heard, the end of the matter is this: I want to worship YOU with awe-filled reverence, knowing that YOU are almighty God and keep YOUR commandments. I know YOU will bring every act to judgment, every hidden and secret thing, whether it is good or evil.','Ecc. 12:13,14',NULL,3,NULL,2,NULL,NULL),(44,'Daily Attitude of my Heart - Thoughts','I will work to destroy every proud obstacle that keeps me from knowing YOU by working consciously to capture my rebellious, self centered thoughts that are not rooted in faith as they enter my mind & teach them to obey YOU.','2 Cor 10:5, 6','Take thoughts & feelings captive.',4,NULL,2,'Win the battles on the inside of me before they get to the outside of me and become fully birthed sin.',NULL),(45,'My Father in Heaven','If a man owns a hundred sheep, and one of them wanders away, will he not leave the ninety-nine on and go to look for the one that wandered off? And if he finds it he is happier about that one sheep than about the ninety-nine that did not wander off. In the same way my Heavenly Father is not willing that any of HIS little ones should be lost. So even if I feel insignificant and alone, God the Father is focused on helping me as if I where they only child HE had!','Matt 18:12-14',NULL,5,NULL,2,'My earthly father was prone to the same sinnful failures as I but YOU will never fail or forsake me ever.',NULL),(46,'I exalt & glorify YOUR holy Name','YOU exist with no boundaries, YOU do not change & are inexhaustible energy & objective truth to whom we must conform through JESUS alone, YOUR ultimate provision for relationship.','desiringGod.com','Last Adam - 1 Corinthians 15:45',6,NULL,2,'YOU are: the great \"I AM\":',NULL),(47,'YOUR Nature','In YOU, I have obtained an inheritance (as an adopted child), having been predestined according to YOUR purpose who works all things according to the counsel of YOUR will.','Eph 1:11',NULL,7,NULL,2,'I worship because YOU are: my perfect Father',NULL),(48,'Scripture reading',NULL,'Psalms',NULL,8,NULL,2,'Read 1 Chapter in the Psalms',NULL),(49,'Yeild to YOU','YOUR Kingdom come (act of waiting & longing for my real home), YOUR will, (timing & desire) be done on earth & in my life as it is in Heaven.','Mat 6:10',NULL,9,NULL,2,'Lead me to YOUR best for me today.',NULL),(50,'Wait on YOU','I am still & know that YOU are God; YOU will be exalted among the nations, YOU will be exalted in the earth.','Ps 46:11:',NULL,10,NULL,2,'Let paitence have her perfect work.',NULL),(51,'Recognize my sin & idoltry','As I bring my specific failures and sorry coming before you, YOU will cleanse me from all the sin that I have committed against YOU and will forgive all my sins of rebellion against YOU.','Lisa Bevere',NULL,11,NULL,2,'In biblical times people would form idols and images, then bow down to what they themselves had crafted. Those with eyes asked guidance of blind idols. Those with breath, mouth, and voice cried out to mute figures with lifeless lips. Those with ears to hear cried out to deaf ears of stone. It sounds like a mistake too obvious to make, but how easily we can do the same!',NULL),(52,'Recognize & replace','Put on: FORGIVING SPIRIT   I will bear with others and forgive one another, if any have grievance against me. I will forgive as YOU forgave me.','Colossians 3:13','Point out anything in me that offends you, and lead me along the path of everlasting life.',12,NULL,2,'Put off: UNFORGIVING SPIRIT   If I will not forgive others, including myself, neither will YOU forgive my sins. Mk 11:26',NULL),(53,'Repent','The fear of the Lord is the beginning of knowledge; fools despise wisdom and instruction.','Proverbs 1:7 ESV','Forgive me of my sins in the exact same way I forgive those that have sinned against me. Mat 6:12 Note repentance and forgiveness run hand in hand. You can\'t have one without the other.',13,NULL,2,'O Lord, hear my voice! Let your ears be attentive to the voice of my pleas for mercy! If you, O LORD, should mark iniquities, O Lord, who could stand? But with YOU there is forgiveness, that YOU may be feared (because of forgiveness I need YOU regularly, where if as judge we were sentenced & sent away there would be no more relationship or desire for one). Our bad şhows YOUR love\'s greatness!  Psalm 130:2-4',NULL),(54,'Release','For “He who would love life And see good days, Let him refrain his tongue from evil, And his lips from speaking deceit. Let him turn away from evil and do good; Let him seek peace and pursue it. For the eyes of the LORD are on the righteous, And His ears are open to their prayers; But the face of the LORD is against those who do evil.”','1 Peter 3:10-12 NKJV',