ay well temporarily not bring me happiness.',NULL),(243,'Daily Attitude of my Heart - Obey','I show YOU my sincere love by keeping YOUR commandments, and they are not a burden.','1 Jh 5:3',NULL,3,NULL,7,'I am an emotional creature & YOU are asking me to set aside my own emotional responses & trust YOU to handle my day as an act of my faith in YOU.',NULL),(244,'Daily Attitude of my Heart - Thoughts','Therefore, I will prepare my mind for action, keep sober in spirit and fix my hope completely on the grace to be brought to me at the revelation of Jesus Christ.','1 Peter 1:13','Take thoughts & feelings captive.',4,NULL,7,'Remember, I am not condemned for the original self-centered, negative, or bad thought when they first comes into my mind. It\'s what I choose to do with those thoughts that produces the sin or not.',NULL),(245,'My Father in Heaven','For I did not receive a spirit that makes me a slave again to fear, but I received the Spirit of adoption. And by way of JESUS I cry, “Abba, Father.” The SPIRIT himself testifies with my spirit that I am God’s child.','Rom 8:15,16',NULL,5,NULL,7,'My earthly and heavenly Father are the 2 most influential relationships in my life for better or worse.',NULL),(246,'I exalt & glorify YOUR holy Name','Think about His omniscience, He knows everything. God is the God of all knowledge. God inhabits eternity. God sees the beginning, the middle and the end. God sees it all at one time. God is all-knowing - He can\'t learn anything. God knows everything that\'s going to happen. Not a blade of grass moves but what He knows it. If you\'re saved, God knew that you would receive the Lord Jesus Christ. Nothing takes God by surprise. God never says, \"Ooops. I never thought of that.\" God is omniscient. I don\'t understand how He swung the stars in the night sky, scooped the oceans and heaped up the mountains or how HE runs this mighty universe. Romans 11:34 says, \"For who hath known the mind of the Lord? or who hath been His counsellor?\"