asks for bread, will give them a stone? Or if they ask for a fish, will give them a snake? If you, though you are evil, know how to give good gifts to your children, how much more will your Father in heaven give good gifts to those who ask him!','Matt 7:9-11',NULL,5,NULL,8,'initiate me as your child.',NULL),(286,'I exalt & glorify YOUR holy Name','El Elyon speaks of the supremacy of God. He is above all. Now, what does El Elyon mean? The word means the strongest of the strong and the highest of the high. Hinduism and Pantheism speak of God as a part of the universe. But God is not a part of the universe. He is the transcendent God. He is above all. He is the Most High God. Jesus is our El Elyon. Colossians 1:16-17 says, \"For by Him were all things created, that are in heaven, and that are in earth, visible and invisible, whether they be thrones, or dominions, or principalities, or powers: all things were created by Him, and for Him: And He is before all things, and by Him all things consist.\" God is above all things. Jesus is our El Elyon.\n-derived from the Hebrew root for “go up” or “ascend,” so the implication is of that which is the very highest. El Elyon denotes exaltation and speaks of absolute right to lordship.','Genesis 14:18-20; Psalm 61:2; 92:1; Daniel 7:25, Deuteronomy 26:19','Consolation of Israel - Luke 2:25',6,NULL,8,'YOU are: EL ELYON [el-el-yohn]: “Most High\"',NULL),(287,'YOUR Nature','Every good gift & every perfect gift is from above, coming down from the Father of lights with whom there is no variation or shadow due to change.','Jam 1:17',NULL,7,NULL,8,'I worship because of YOUR: Goodness',NULL),(288,'Scripture reading',NULL,'Psalms',NULL,8,NULL,8,'Read 1 Chapter in the Psalms',NULL),(289,'Yeild to YOU','May YOUR Kingdom come which is my home and YOUR will be done on earth & in my life as quickly & completely as it is in Heaven.','Mat 6:10',NULL,9,NULL,8,'Guide me in a great adventure for YOUR glory today.',NULL),(290,'Wait on YOU','YOU are my