thy and true.”','Rev 21:1-27',NULL,32,NULL,11,'Journal what You said to me today:',NULL),(433,'Benidiction for my day','In all these things I am more than a conqueror through YOU who loves me. For I am sure that neither death nor life, nor angels nor rulers, nor things present nor things to come, nor powers, nor height nor depth, nor anything else in all creation, will be able to separate me from YOUR love in Christ Jesus my Lord. Score, in JESUS I win!!','Rom 8:37-39',NULL,33,NULL,11,NULL,NULL),(434,'Music with meaning.','A Psalm for giving thanks. Make a joyful noise to YOU, all earth! Serve YOU with gladness! Come to YOUR presence with singing!','Psalm 100:1-2',NULL,34,NULL,11,'Music has the power to communicate messages and emotions that words cannot effectively capture.','https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLZdpE0NYhNb8oTRuuAgPt6OG0SuWcMZUK'),(435,'Pray for specific people.',NULL,NULL,'Customer user input will soon be available here.',35,NULL,11,'Who would you have me pray for right now? (fill names in below)',NULL),(436,'Forgivness','Forgive me of my sins in the exact same way I forgive those that have sinned against me.',NULL,NULL,36,NULL,11,NULL,NULL),(437,'My List',NULL,NULL,NULL,37,NULL,11,'This will be a list of people I am praying for.',NULL),(438,'Worship & Praise -YOUR Name',NULL,'Matthew 6:9',NULL,38,NULL,11,'I exalt & glorify YOUR holy Name:',NULL),(439,'Replace my way with YOUR way, I receive:',NULL,NULL,'Custom user input will soon be available here.',39,NULL,11,NULL,NULL),(440,'Personal Requests',NULL,NULL,NULL,40,NULL,11,'list burdens & concerns I am praying for:',NULL),(441,'Daily Attitude of my Heart - Sacrifice','If I try to save my life I will lose it, but if I lose my life for YOUR sake I will find it. For what will it profit me if I gain the whole world and forfeit my soul? Or what shall I give in return for my soul?','Matthew 16:25-26',NULL,1,NULL,12,'I present myself as a living sacrifice, Spirit fill & use me today.',NULL),(442,'Daily