e instructed that in returning (repentence??) and rest I shall be saved; in quietness and in trust shall be my strength. Lord, I am willing!','‭‭Isaiah‬ ‭30:15‬ ‭ESV‬‬',NULL,10,NULL,12,'I am waiting & consciously pausing so YOU can take the lead today.',NULL),(451,'Recognize my sin & idoltry','Then I will cry out to YOU,== but YOU will not answer. Instead, YOU will hide YOUR face from me at that time if I have practiced evil deeds.','Micah 3:4',NULL,11,NULL,12,'Here’s what’s going on: They are declaring, “Yahweh is our God. Yahweh saved us from Egypt. Yahweh is our Lord,” yet they are worshiping an idol. We must see this warning, because if they could have all the right declarations while still worshiping an idol, we can too.',NULL),(452,'Recognize & replace','Put on: RESPONSIBILITY.  If I can be trusted with very little I can also be trusted with much, and if I am dishonest with very little I am also dishonest with much.','Luke 16:10','Test me, Lord, and try me, examine my heart and my mind.  Psalm 26:2',12,NULL,12,'Put off: IRRESPONSIBILITY   If I have not been trustworthy with someone else’s property, who will give me property of my own? Lk 16:12',NULL),(453,'Repent','Teach me your way, O Lord, that I may walk in YOUR truth; unite my heart to fear YOUR name.','Psalm 86:11 ESV','Now I beg YOU, forgive my sin and come back with me, so that I may worship YOU.  1 Samuel 15:25',13,NULL,12,'John bevere take on repentance.Repentance means changing my mind so deeply that it changes our personality from the core of my being. When I turn to Christ, He makes me brand new, giving me the grace to live like Him.',NULL),(454,'Release','Yet the righteous will hold to his way, And he who has clean hands will be stronger and stronger.','Job 17:9 NKJV',NULL,14,NULL,12,'YOU will forgive my iniquity, & YOU will remember my sin no more.  Jer 31:34',NULL),(455,'Scripture reading',NULL,'Proverbs',NULL,15,NULL,12,'Read 1 Chapter in the Proverbs',NULL),(456,'Pray for One Another','We ough