ient for today with no worry for tomorrow.',NULL),(463,'Personal -specific issues','have not because you all not',NULL,'I would like to cast on YOU now the following issues that I personally need YOU to deal with in my day today: 1 Pet 5:6-11',23,NULL,12,NULL,NULL),(464,'Personal -$$','I honor YOU with my wealth and with the firstfruits of all I produce; then my barns will be filled with plenty, and my vats will be bursting with wine.','Proverbs 3:9-10',NULL,24,NULL,12,NULL,NULL),(465,'Personal -power of my words','What I have said in the dark will be heard in the daylight, and what I have whispered in the ear in the inner rooms will be proclaimed from the roofs.','Luke 12:3','Let your speech always be gracious, seasoned with salt, so that you may know how you ought to answer each person.  Colossians 4:6 ESV',25,NULL,12,'When a man is filled with the Word of God you cannot keep him still, If a man has got the Word, he must speak or die. Dwight L. Moody',NULL),(466,'Personal -Who am I?','I am led by YOUR Spirit therefore I am YOUR child. For I did not receive the spirit of slavery to fall back into fear, but I have received the Spirit of adoption as sons, by whom I cry, \"Abba! Father!\"','Rom 8:14, 15','Remind me WHO I AM because of YOU JESUS:',26,NULL,12,'I am led by the Spirit of God',NULL),(467,'My Life Purpose','YOUR plans for me are plans for welfare and not for evil, to give me a future and a hope.','Jeremiah 29:11','Who is God to me?',27,NULL,12,'I always wanted to be somebody. Now I realize I should have been more specific. -Lily Tomlin\nThe glory of God is a human being fully alive. -Irenaeus\nA healthy sefl-image is seeing yourself as God sees you. No more, no less.',NULL),(468,'Thanks','YOUR steadfast love never ceases; YOUR mercies never come to an end; they are new every morning; great is YOUR faithfulness. \"YOU are my portion,\" says my soul, \"therefore I will hope in YOU.\"','Lam 3:22-24',NULL,28,NULL,12,NULL,NULL),(469,'Scripture reading',NULL,'NT'